notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Slightly more stomata at edges, fewer in middle. Central keel with more hair, otherwise bicellular microhairs and prickles fairly uniform.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margins with only a few hairs, mainly in two stripes, keels hairy, sulcus densely hairy

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Stomatal zone with few papillae, interstomatal zones with many papillae and hairs. Fewer papillae towards apex.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margins with only a few hairs, keels hairy, sulcus densely hairy. Only a few stomata, including some in sulcus.

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Nearly glabrous to glabrous near margins, with mix of long prickle hairs and bicellular microhairs in center. A few macrohairs in center. Stomata generally infrequent, more common near center.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Two stripes of hair along margin, keels hairy and sulcus very densely hairy, very few stomata on margin

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Nearly glabrous, more prickle hairs at edges of lemma. Stomata occurring in rows.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. A few hairs on palea margins. Densely hairy in sulcus, keels ciliolate.

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Few prickle hairs, nearly glabrous, with many rows of stomata.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margins nearly glabrous. Keels ciliate, sulcus densely hairy.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Papillae, prickles, and bicellular microhairs in interstomatal bands, stomatal bands with few papillae. Fewer papillae at base of lemma.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Margins with prickles, keels, sulcus hairy.

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Glabrous, only a few stomata present except in one band
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margins with prickles and bicellular microhairs, keels hairy, sulcus with a few macrohairs mixed with bicellular microhairs and prickles, but hairs not dense

notes_lemma: Papillae present but uncommon. Prickles and a few papillae in interstomatal bands, stomata more common at center of lemma and rare at margins.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margins glabrous. Keels ciliate, sulcus hairy.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Somewhat more hairs, especially bicellular microhairs, towards the margins. Fewer papillae at margins.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Two densely hairy keels, sulcus with sparse hair. Very dense stomata on outer keel ridges. Much of surface covered in papillae.

notes_lemma: Papillae present; papillae and stomata frequent. Prickle hairs fairly uniformally distributed.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Sulcus relatively similar to margin. Keels lack dense stomata.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. More hairs at edges, especially prickles.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Margins with prickle hairs and bicellular microhairs. Sulcus with prickles, bicellular microhairs, and macrohairs. Stomatal bands have fewer papillae, although there are papillae-less bands without stomata as well.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Stomatal bands mostly without papillae or prickles. Prickles and a few bicellular microhairs in interstomatal bands.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Margins with a few prickle and bicellular microhairs. Sulcus similar to margin, with only a few macrohairs. Keels with macrohairs present.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Cilia at apex. Stomatal bands with fewer papillae. Relatively few stomata.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Sulcus with many more macrohairs than margins, densely hairy.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Stomatal bands with fewer papillae.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Sulcus with many more macrohairs than margins. Many stomata.

notes_lemma: Papillae present. Stomatal zones with fewer papillae and prickles.
notes_palea: Papillae present. Sulcus with more macrohairs than margins. No bicellular microhairs seen. Many stomata.

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Glabrous, only a few cilia at top.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margin with only a few prickles, keels only ciliate at apex. Sulcus densely hairy with many macrohairs.

notes_lemma: Papillae present, especially in areas with more hairs. Macrohairs common in center. Prickle hairs also present nearer margins.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Prickle hairs mainly in two loose rows in center of margin and in sulcus, margins otherwise fairly smooth. Sulcus also has macrohairs, although not dense compared to other species. Short hairs present on keels.

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Many stomata most places except near margins.
notes_palea: Papillae absent, stomata rare. Margins with some prickle hairs, rare microhairs. Sulcus hairy, with prickle hairs and macrohairs as well as rare stomata. Keels not well defined, but hairy.

notes_lemma: Papillae present, mainly near edges, most stomata limited to a few rows near edges.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Prickle and bicellular microhairs limited to middle and edges of margins. Lots of prickles, macrohairs, and longer bicellular microhairs in sulcus. Stomata infrequent on margins but more frequent in sulcus. Keels somewhat hairy.

notes_lemma: Papillae present throughout, fewer in stomatal bands. Dense macrohairs and prickles in interstomatal bands.
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Margin mostly glabrous, a couple bicellular microhairs and prickle hairs present. Keels ciliate, sulcus with some macrohairs, bicellular microhairs, and prickles. A few stomata present.

notes_lemma: Papillae absent. Hairs primarily at margins and center
notes_palea: Papillae absent. Ciliate near apex. A few bicellular microhairs and many prickles on margins. Sulcus is full of dense macrohairs with some prickles and bicellular microhairs. Only a few scattered stomata.
